<br>
I was just wondering if some of you RZ folks could give me some information about your server.  After about 9months of blue, and 3months of TZ/VZ... I left eq for a while.<br>
<br>
Coming back now I have started a Rogue on a blue server with some friends.  Yet my hunger for combat is coming back.<br>
<br>
At the time of my leaving TZ/VZ the coin only had recently been implemented and the crossteaming was growing ....<br>
<br>
<br>
My character experiences include most all classes into the teens, my high been a 30wiz.  I am quite familiar with the harsh reality of PvP, and even with the 1 item loot.<br>
<br>
I was just wondering what life is like on RZ, on the team servers it was obviously team driven combat, with some multi-team guilds (grrrrr bastards)<br>
<br>
