<br>
Anyhow, any info would be great... I am also debating what class to make there if I start.  My experiences as a wizard might come in handy, but I'm leaning toward rogue, or perhaps Necro....<br>
<br>
Thanks. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ucoyoteblack.showPublicProfile?language=EN>coyoteblack</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif BORDER=0 HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(1/10/01 8:40:07 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=70.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Tell me of Rallos</span><hr size=1>      I will try to answer you questions. First I am in my 32 season as a Rogue on RAllos. It is all for nothing server if you don't like them and they are in your level range you can kill them. The first 10 levels are a test of your will to succeed as everyone from 1 to 5 seems to think it is Quake. And 5 to 10 at least you can defend you self better but it is still the same.<br>
