am killing newbies in gfay,freeport,queynos so for a new person to the server it could get very frustrating. Things stay bad till about 35. Then you get a break to 47 when the 51 wizzies get torrent and show rogues and other melees a hearty ass whoopin. Once at that level snare poisons are a must, youll never land normal snare/root item or engulfing darkness proc on people then. People keep the MR too high, My MR is 115 in normal hunting gear and thats still way below most people of the same level. 50-60 is pvp hell time. Unless you feel like sacrificing your dignity and join one of the bjs for loot and protection organizations your gonna end up in guild wars and random pk target to the portal campers. The server is fun, its got the edge alot of people crave, and the feeling of waxing that smack talker and taking his fbss is the greatest thing in the virtual world. Ya gotta be thick skinned to play this server, and if you can take it its great fun.<br>
